        <h2 class='static-page__subtitle static-page__subtitle--sinai'>Catalogues and Handlists</h2>
​
        <p class="static-page__text static-page__text--sinai">The following catalogues and handlists were consulted in creating the descriptive metadata for the manuscripts published through the Sinai Manuscripts Digital Library website.</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Aland = Aland, K. <i>Kurzgefasste Liste der griechischen Handschriften des Neuen Testaments</i>. Berlin: De Gruyter, 1963, rev. ed. 1994. [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/32035214', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Aleksidze, et al. = Aleksidze, Z., et al. <i>Catalogue of Georgian manuscripts discovered in 1975 at St. Catherine&#39;s Monastery on Mount Sinai</i>. Athens, 2005. [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/1131665083', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Atiya = Atiya, Aziz Suryal. <i>The Arabic Manuscripts of Mount Sinai: A Hand-List of the Arabic Manuscripts and Scrolls Microfilmed at the Library of the Monastery of St. Catherine, Mount Sinai</i>. Johns Hopkins Press, 1955. [<%= link_to 'Internet Archive', 'https://archive.org/details/arabicmanuscript0000atiy_m0l2/mode/2up', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Balageorgos and Kriticou = Balageorgos and Kriticou. <i>Les manuscrits de musique byzantine: Sina&iuml;</i>. Athens, 2008. [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/660172233', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Brock 1995 = S.P. Brock. <i>Catalogue of Syriac Fragments (New Finds) in the Library of the Monastery of St Catherine, Mount Sinai</i> (Athens, 1995). [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/title/catalogue-of-syriac-fragments-new-finds-in-the-library-of-the-monastery-of-saint-catherine-mount-sinai/oclc/780492566', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Clark = Clark, Kenneth W., ed. <i>Checklist of Manuscripts in St. Catherine&rsquo;s Monastery Mount Sinai. </i>Washington, D.C.: Library of Congress, 1952. [<%= link_to 'Library of Congress', 'https://www.loc.gov/item/52060038', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Gardthausen = Gardthausen, V. E. <i>Catalogus codicum Graecorum Sinaiticorum</i>. Oxford, 1886. [<%= link_to 'Internet Archive', 'https://archive.org/details/cataloguscodicu00sinagoog', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>G&eacute;hin 2006= G&eacute;hin, Paul. &ldquo;Manuscrits sina&iuml;tiques dispers&eacute;s, I: les fragments arabes et syriaques de Paris.&rdquo; <i>OC</i> 90 (2006): 23-43. [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/title/-manuscrits-sinaitiques-disperses-i-les-fragments-syriaques-et-arabes-de-paris/oclc/784157423', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>G&eacute;hin 2009 = G&eacute;hin, Paul. &quot;Fragments patristiques syriaques des Nouvelles d&eacute;couvertes du Sina&iuml;.&quot; <i>Collectanea Christiana Orientalia</i> 6 (2009): 67-93</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>G&eacute;hin 2017 = G&eacute;hin, Paul. <i>Les manuscrits syriaques de parchemin du Sina&iuml; et leurs</i> membra disjecta (CSCO 665, Subsidia 136; Leuven, 2017). [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/title/manuscrits-syriaques-de-parchemin-du-sinai-et-leurs-membra-disjecta/oclc/1000455293', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Gibson = Gibson, Margaret Dunlop. <i>Catalogue of the Arabic Manuscripts in the Convent of S. Catharine on Mount Sinai</i>. Cambridge University Press, 1894.[<%= link_to 'Internet Archive', 'https://archive.org/details/catalogueofarabi00sainrich', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Greek New Finds = Nikolopoulos, P. G. &Tau;&alpha; &nu;&#941;&alpha; &epsilon;&upsilon;&rho;&#942;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&alpha; &tau;&omicron;&upsilon; &Sigma;&iota;&nu;&#940; (Athens, 1998). English translation: A. Hatzopoulos, The New Finds of Sinai (Athens, 1999). [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/title/new-finds-of-sinai/oclc/913489510', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Kamil = K&#257;mil, Mur&#257;d. <i>Catalogue of All Manuscripts in the Monastery of St. Catherine on Mount Sinai</i>. Harrassowitz, 1970. [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/title/catalogue-of-all-manuscripts-in-the-monastery-of-st-catharine-on-mount-sinai/oclc/859613867', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Lewis = Lewis, Agnes Smith. <i>Catalogue of the Syriac Manuscripts in the Convent of Saint Catherine on Mount Sinai</i>. Cambridge University Press, 1894. [<%= link_to 'Internet Archive', 'https://archive.org/details/catalogueofsyria00sainrich', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>LOC = <i>Manuscripts in St. Catherine&#39;s Monastery, Mount Sinai</i>. Library of Congress. [<%= link_to 'Library of Congress', 'https://www.loc.gov/collections/manuscripts-in-st-catherines-monastery-mount-sinai', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Meimaris = Meimaris, Yiannis E. <i>Katalogos ton neon aravikon cheirographon tes Hieras Mones Hagias Aikaterines tou Orous Sina = Kataluy al-Majtutat al-&rsquo;arabiyya al-muktasafa haditan bi-Dayr Sant Katarin al-muqaddas</i>. Ethnikon Hidryma Ereunon, 1985. [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/title/katalogos-ton-neon-aravikon-cheirographon-tes-hieras-mones-hagias-aikaterines-tou-orous-sina-kataluy-al-majtutat-al-arabiyya-al-muktasafa-haditan-bi-dayr-sant-katarin-al-muqaddas/oclc/1123922473', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>NLI = <i>Manuscripts in the Holy Monastery of St. Catherine at Mount Sinai</i>. National Library of Israel.</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Perria = Perria, Lidia. <i>Repertorio dei manoscritti greci di area orientale, palestino-sinaitica</i>. Messina, 2000. [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/1158454955', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
​
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>Philoth&eacute;e 2008 = Philoth&eacute;e du Sina&iuml;, <i>Nouveaux manuscrits syriaques du Sina&iuml;</i>(Athens, 2008). [<%= link_to 'WorldCat', 'https://www.worldcat.org/title/nouveaux-manuscrits-syriaques-du-sinai/oclc/476756980', class: 'si-link' %>]</p>
